data.description: BEST NEIGHBORHOOD IN SE CAPE! DIRECT GULF ACCESS - with a private dock, electric boat lift, and easy access to open water! NO FLOOD ZONE and NO FLOOD INSURANCE REQUIRED! NEW ROOF in June 2023 with 3rd nail retrofitting - this provides extra protection during high winds and saves additional money on insurance. Three bedroom, two bath, open concept home with high-end finishes, newer stainless-steel appliances and newer washer and dryer. This peaceful home is the perfect retreat for those seeking an upscale waterfront lifestyle. Serene outdoor living space for entertaining guests poolside or simply relaxing and enjoying the views. Large windows provide natural light with custom-remote-controlled window treatments throughout. Home has a large front and back yard, circular driveway and is on dead end street. Minutes from dining, entertainment & shopping. Close to Downtown Fort Myers over the Midpoint Bridge less than a mile away. Fabulous rental income potential when you're not enjoying the home yourself with no lease restrictions and no HOA. **No flooding from Hurricane Ian** New soffits and new gutters to be installed soon.
